snippet.title: 100 Bullets [Acclaim - CANCELLED! XBOX & PS2]
snippet.description:
http://www.unseen64.net

Acclaim announced plans to release a video game based on 100 Bullets. However, following the collapse of Acclaims publishing house, the game has essentially been cancelled.

Music from Jet Set Radio Future OST
